the same position to argue on his behalf as it was for mrs parish 
who is britishborn but it said it was appealing on bazofts 
behalf for humanitarian reasons and because he lived in britain for 
years 
the explosion at the military complex was reported in london to 
have killed up to 700 people but the iraqis later said 19 people 
were killed in a fuel depot blast 
